<body>
    <nav><div class="nav-inner"><a href="/">securemycameras</a></div></nav>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="updated">Last updated: March 18, 2026</p>

        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>securemycameras.com is operated by Salish Private Estates LLC. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website or purchase our products.</p>

        <h2>What We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Email address</strong> — if you submit the quiz or purchase the guide</li>
            <li><strong>Quiz responses</strong> — your answers and score (not personally identifiable)</li>
            <li><strong>Payment information</strong> — processed entirely by Paddle (our payment processor). We never see or store your credit card details.</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics data</strong> — anonymous page views via Cloudflare Web Analytics (no cookies, no personal data)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To deliver the product you purchased</li>
            <li>To send a follow-up email with security tips based on your quiz results (if you submitted your email)</li>
            <li>To improve our products and website</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Paddle</strong> — payment processing (<a href="https://www.paddle.com/legal/privacy">Paddle Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
            <li><strong>Kit (ConvertKit)</strong> — email delivery (<a href="https://kit.com/privacy">Kit Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
            <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — hosting and analytics (<a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/">Cloudflare Privacy Policy</a>)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>We do not use tracking cookies. Cloudflare Web Analytics is privacy-first and does not use cookies or collect personal data.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may request deletion of your data at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:inquiry@salishsecurity.ai">inquiry@salishsecurity.ai</a>. We will process your request within 30 days.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>For privacy questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:inquiry@salishsecurity.ai">inquiry@salishsecurity.ai</a>.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
